{
 "name": "RPlog_Karrde_Visits",
 "title": "Karrde Visits",
 "summary": "At his Myrkr base, smuggler chief Talon Karrde drops by the guest barracks to check on Jessalyn Valios, who confides a sensitive discovery: something alive in the forest blocks the Force for anyone adept, herself and Simon included. Karrde files the unsettling information away and they agree to keep it from Simon, whom Jessalyn does not yet trust. The mechanic Orson then arrives, grease-covered from repairing the battered ships, and he and Karrde step into the hall for a heavier, more personal conversation. Pressed by Orson quiet disapproval, the cornered Karrde admits he can no longer tell what is right, that Luke has not answered his calls, and that simply giving in would be easier -- before, weary and out of answers, he leaves for a long walk.",
